These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, salsa, r&b, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, thai, polish, french
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, taxi, roller
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the thai and the fan of country##2
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the polish is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country    | r&b      | salsa      | jazz    |
| Nationality   | french | canadian | thai | polish |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | roller       | taxi     | scooter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, grapefruit, onion, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, gardening, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, crime, sports
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | spinach     | grapes     | grapefruit       | onion    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening   | drawing | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | crime | animation    | martial-arts        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, juice, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, american, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, volleyball, ice-hockey
1. the german is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the canadian##3
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the american is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up  | juice    | tea |
| Nationality   | american   | nigerian  | canadian  | german    |
| Sport         | rowing    | ice-hockey | snowboarding | volleyball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, grapefruit, banana, carrot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, western, superhero
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, hamster, mouse
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person eating apple##2
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating banana##1
4. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is the person eating carrot##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | banana   | apple     | grapefruit | carrot |
| Movie-Genre   | western | superhero | epic   | martial-arts     |
| Pet           | mouse | hamster      | goldfish     | rabbit       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, asparagus, orange, banana
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, nurse, doctor, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, sports, martial-arts, epic
1. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
3. the doctor is the person watching animation movies##1
4. the software-developer is between the person eating orange and the person eating asparagus##2
5. the doctor is on the right of the accountant##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating banana##1
7. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
8. the person eating orange is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
9. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | orange      | banana | asparagus      | zucchini |
| Job           | nurse | software-developer | accountant | doctor   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | epic   | sports     | animation   |

