.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, project-manager, firefighter, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, r&b, soul, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, swimming, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is basketball is the social-worker##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the project-manager is on the right of the fan of house##1
8. the project-manager is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | social-worker    | project-manager   | firefighter | lawyer |
| Music-Genre   | house     | soul   | hip-hop         | r&b        |
| Sport         | basketball | lacrosse | swimming         | skateboarding       |

