.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, hiking, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, architect, journalist, firefighter
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, canadian, spanish, malaysian
 1. the canadian is on the left or right of the russian##3
 2. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 4. the journalist is on the right of the spanish##1
 5. the spanish is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 9. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the architect is on the left or right of the journalist##3
11. the architect is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | hiking    | magic-tricks  | collecting | reading   |
| Job           | firefighter | architect   | journalist    | engineer |
| Nationality   | malaysian      | spanish | canadian | russian  |

