.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, nectarine, spinach, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, photography, traveling, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, crime, time-travel, musical
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | spinach | nectarine    | kale | orange    |
| Hobby         | traveling     | collecting | photography  | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | musical      | documentary   | time-travel         |

