The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, freelancer, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, mystery, time-travel, horror
1. the architect is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the mechanic##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
4. the freelancer is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the writer is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | iced-tea            | 7up     | hot-chocolate      |
| Job           | mechanic    | writer | freelancer     | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | time-travel    | mystery | horror    |

