.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi, asparagus, cucumber
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, adventure, epic, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, polish, colombian
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the turkish##3
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the person watching spy movies is the person eating cucumber##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the polish##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
