.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, mechanic, scientist, nurse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, thriller, satire, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, cycling, skiing
1. the mechanic is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the nurse##3
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the scientist is on the right of the teacher##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
7. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | nurse | mechanic        | teacher   | scientist  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller             | superhero     | musical | satire  |
| Sport         | badminton           | skiing | baseball   | cycling |

