.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, almond-milk, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, pilot, librarian, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, train, van
1. the analyst is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the librarian##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the librarian##3
6. the person driving the van is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking water##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the pilot##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea   | almond-milk   | water    | fanta |
| Job         | pilot | librarian    | architect      | analyst |
| Transport   | quad-bike      | van | train | bus   |

