.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, photography, baking, magic-tricks
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, ship, van
1. the person drinking water is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the van##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person drinking water##1
9. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | lemonade      | water | juice       | cola  |
| Hobby       | baking | gardening | magic-tricks    | photography |
| Transport   | tram     | bike         | ship | van     |

