3. the pilot is on the far left or far right##3
4. the pilot is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the videographer is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
6. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the person eating peach is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
