4. the owner of the mouse is between the videographer and the spanish##2
5. the videographer is the indian##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the indian##3
7. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the social-worker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
