.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, traveling, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the skateboard##2
5. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | mirinda    | fanta      | water |
| Hobby       | skydiving  | drawing | sudoku | traveling     |
| Transport   | trike | quad-bike        | skateboard  | taxi        |

