3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the airplane and the person drinking soy-milk##2
6. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
