.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, water, tea
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, grapes, pepper, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian, colombian, american
1. the american is on the left of the canadian##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the canadian##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the colombian##1
8. the person eating pomegranate is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | tea    | cola | water  |
| Food          | grapes          | pomegranate | artichoke       | pepper      |
| Nationality   | colombian     | brazilian    | american     | canadian |

