.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, kale, apple, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, photographer, dressmaker, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, parkour, basketball
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is the person eating pepper##1
4. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person eating spinach and the person eating apple##2
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
8. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | apple | kale  | spinach  | pepper           |
| Job     | paramedic | dressmaker | photographer   | software-developer |
| Sport   | basketball   | snowboarding       | rugby | parkour  |

 